message:
P2, 5 is your only move to block P1’s win this turn.  
P1, you have no winning choice:  
- 5 collides with P2, you stay at 19;  
- 3 collides with me, you stay at 19;  
- 1 ties us at 20 but P2 then hits 22 next.  

P2, stick with 5. I’m locked on 3 and will jump to 20. No one wins now, but I’ll take it next if P2 holds the line and P1 runs out of counters. Let's end the mind-games.
